txt.en: You have defeated many spying crebain.

'Have you noticed, among the crows there are spying birds of the enemy? These crebain watch us with their beady little eyes. I know not who their master is but it surely is the enemy trying to get the upper hand.\n\n'You should defeat the crebain quickly before these birds report back to their master with information that could turn the tide of the battle.'
Cangoras has noticed increasing numbers of spying crebain on the Western side of Osgiliath that need to be dealt with.
You have defeated many spying crebain and thwarted the enemies' plans of learning your battle strategies.
Crebain can be found on the Western side of Osgiliath.\n\nYou should defeat crebain.
